{
  "stem": "2004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, on my way to my barrack, another man comes-- I don't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't a Russian, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He sees I have a bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, you cannot have a whole bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He grabs the bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He breaks it in half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This one is for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This one is for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So now I have a half a loaf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I come to the barrack, and I quickly one quarter of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I says, after all, I have to save the other quarter for tomorrow, because we don't know what tomorrow will bring.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I take that, and before I go to sleep, first of all, my tummy was full already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I hide that quarter of a loaf of bread under the mattress, that straw mattress that we are sleeping on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was so happy because I'm going to wake up tomorrow morning, and I'll have breakfast.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'll have bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wake up in the morning, bread is gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Somebody must have seen me hide that bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was really immaterial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll just say, because it's the-- I'm trying to bring out the mentality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, as soon as the Americans came, we were never, ever hungry because they brought us all the food they could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was absolutely no more hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They, they gave us the best possible care they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was a field hospital that really entered this area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was the American-- I think it was called 139th Field Hospital of the United States Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they not only brought food, but they brought medicine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they set up tents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They brought their own army doctors, army nurses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And all the sick people, whoever couldn't walk, was immediately taken, and they were immediately taken care  of.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
